'''水管工'''（{{lang-en|plumber}}）是一種專門從事安裝及維修[[水管|水管]]系統，包括[[食水|食水]]、[[污水|污水]]及[[排水|排水]]系統的[[職業|職業]]<ref>Whitney, William D., ed.. "Trade." Def, 7. ''The Century Dictionary: An Encyclopedic Lexicon of the English Language'' vol. 8. New York. The Century Co. 1895. 6,415. Print.</ref><ref name="MichReport">[http://milmi.org/Portals/137/publications/Employment_Occupations_Skilled_Trades_Michigan.pdf Employment and Occupations in the Skilled Trades in Michigan] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171201042545/http://milmi.org/Portals/137/publications/Employment_Occupations_Skilled_Trades_Michigan.pdf |date=2017-12-01 }}, Michigan Department of Technology, Management, and Budget, Bureau of Labor Market Information and Strategic Initiatives (June 2013).</ref>。

==歷史==
水管工的英語「{{lang|en|plumber}}」可追溯至[[羅馬帝國|羅馬帝國]]時期<ref>Pulsifer, William H. [https://archive.org/details/notesforhistoryo00pulsrich Notes For a History of Lead], New York University Press, 1888 pp. 132, 158</ref> 。[[鉛|鉛]]的[[拉丁語|拉丁語]]是「{{lang|la|plumbum}}」。因為[[羅馬人|羅馬人]]的管道和排水管中均會使用鉛<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=Px4XAAAAYAAJ&pg=RA1-PA821 |title=Middleton, The Remains of Ancient Rome, Vol. 2, A & C Black, 1892 |accessdate=2020-09-03 |archive-date=2020-08-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200819200143/https://books.google.com/books?id=Px4XAAAAYAAJ&pg=RA1-PA821 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，有些屋頂甚至會用鉛覆蓋。鉛同時也用於[[管道|管道]]和製造[[浴室|浴室]]<ref>[https://web.archive.org/web/20081121025509/http://www.ila-lead.org/factbook/annex.pdf Historical production and uses of lead]. ila-lead.org</ref> 。

從中世紀[[威斯敏斯特宮|威斯敏斯特宮]]修理屋頂的施工記錄中可以看出，任何從事鉛加工的人都被稱為「plumber」。施工記錄形容水管工「用鉛覆蓋貯藏室的屋頂，以及小廳屋頂的各種缺陷」<ref name="plum1">{{cite book|title=The history of the ancient palace and late Houses of Parliament at Westminster|year=1836|publisher=J B Nichols and son|page=[https://archive.org/details/bub_gb_DQc3AAAAMAAJ/page/n141 122]|url=https://archive.org/details/bub_gb_DQc3AAAAMAAJ|author=EW Wedlake|author2=J Britton |accessdate=28 June 2010|chapter=Westminster Palace}}</ref> 。因此，具有鉛加工專業知識的人初頭被稱為「plumbarius」，後來簡稱為「plumber」。

==工作內容==
[[File:Working_underground.jpg|thumb]]離開[[下水道|下水道]]]]
要成為一個熟練的水管工，需要多年訓練及工作經驗。某些國家及地區更要求水喉匠必須獲得許可。日常水管工需要：
*閱讀圖則和規格，以決定[[供水|供水]]，[[污水|污水]]和通風系統的佈局
*找出管道設備和系統中的故障，並正確診斷故障原因
*安裝，維修和保養家用，商用和工業用水管裝置和系統
*連接管道，定位和標記位置
*使用工具測量、切割、彎曲和穿線管道
*使用各種零件，將管道和配件焊接在一起
*使用氣壓表和水壓表測試管道是否有洩漏問題
*認識法律對水管的法規和確保施工安全
*確保工程符合安全標準和建築法規

==各地規管==
===美國===

[[美國|美國]]每個[[州_(美国)|州]]和地區可能都有自己不同的水管工許可制度和稅收計劃。一些州會分別發出水喉匠或水喉技工執照，而其他州則僅發出熟手水管工執照。要得到水管工執照，水管工要接受培訓，經驗達到一定標準。多數需要通過考試<ref>{{cite web |title=How to Become a Plumber |url=https://www.howtobecome.com/how-to-become-a-plumber |website=www.howtobecome.com |accessdate=2020-09-03 |language=en |archive-date=2019-08-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190829085138/https://www.howtobecome.com/how-to-become-a-plumber |dead-url=no }}</ref>。聯邦法律沒有強制規定水管工需要有許可證<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.bls.gov/ooh/construction-and-extraction/plumbers-pipefitters-and-steamfitters.htm#tab-4|title=How to Become a Plumber in the USA|last=|first=|date=1 November 2016|work=|publisher=U.S. Bureau of Labor Statistics|newspaper=|location=|pages=|language=|via=|accessdate=1 November 2016|archive-date=2020-08-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200828222759/https://www.bls.gov/OOH/construction-and-extraction/plumbers-pipefitters-and-steamfitters.htm#tab-4|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===加拿大===
在[[加拿大|加拿大]]，牌照制度因省而異。但是各省有共同製定牌照指南，確保所有省份的學徒培訓標準一致。「Red Seal」計劃是一項評估加拿大技工技能的計劃。擁有「Red Seal」證書代表該技工的能力水平符合該行業的國家標準<ref>{{cite web |last1=Canada |first1=Employment and Social Development |title=Red Seal Program |url=http://www.red-seal.ca/about/pr.4gr.1m-eng.html |website=www.red-seal.ca |accessdate=2020-09-03 |archive-date=2020-08-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200802171744/http://www.red-seal.ca/about/pr.4gr.1m-eng.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===英國===
{{link-en|英國國家職業資格證書|National Vocational Qualifications}} 於2008年前為[[英國|英國]]主要的水管工認證制度，但後來被「資歷與學分架構」取代。2015年，英國設立[[資歷架構|資歷架構]]取代「資歷與學分架構」。英國的水管工需要通過{{link-en|英国伦敦城市行业协会|City and Guilds of London Institute}}的二級及三級資歷。除了英国伦敦城市行业协会，[[培生集團|培生集團]]亦有提供水管工資歷考試<ref>{{cite web | last = | first = | title =Plumbing Qualifications in the UK | newspaper = | location = | pages = | language = | publisher =Local Heroes | url =https://www.localheroes.com/advice/how-to-become-a-plumber | accessdate =27 February 2018 | archive-date =2018-06-12 | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20180612142534/https://www.localheroes.com/advice/how-to-become-a-plumber | dead-url =no }}</ref>。

=== 愛爾蘭 ===
水管學徒需要通過4年[[學徒制|學徒制]]和資格考試才能成為專業水管工。通過資格考試對企業認證一名水管工的信譽和經驗很有幫助。[[愛爾蘭|愛爾蘭]]亦有水管工協會<ref>{{cite web |title=APHCI {{!}} Association of Plumbers & Heating Contractors Ireland |url=https://www.aphci.ie/ |website=www.aphci.ie |accessdate=2020-09-03 |archive-date=2019-03-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190326203848/https://www.aphci.ie/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，方便顧客尋找有信譽的水管工。

===香港===
香港《水務設施條例》規定只有「持牌水喉匠」或「註冊水喉技工」才可以建造、安裝、保養、更改、修理或拆除消防供水系統或內部供水系統<ref>{{cite web |title=水務署 - 持牌水喉匠 |url=https://www.wsd.gov.hk/tc/plumbing-engineering/licensed-plumbers/index.html |website=www.wsd.gov.hk |accessdate=2020-09-03 |archive-date=2019-10-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191022034152/https://www.wsd.gov.hk/tc/plumbing-engineering/licensed-plumbers/index.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。香港政府亦有設立水喉匠牌照諮詢委員會，專門處理水喉匠牌照事宜。

==危險==
水管工面對很多類型的危險，例如異物入眼，肌肉會勞損和扭傷，皮膚會割傷、[[瘀傷|瘀傷]]、挫傷、燒傷和[[燙傷|燙傷]]，甚至會[[骨折|骨折]]和[[疝氣|疝氣]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://fraser.stlouisfed.org/files/docs/publications/bls/bls_1079_1952.pdf |title="Injuries  and  Accident  Causes in  Plumbing  Operations" United States Department of Labor. 1949 |accessdate=2020-09-03 |archive-date=2017-05-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170528221647/https://fraser.stlouisfed.org/files/docs/publications/bls/bls_1079_1952.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref> 。
如果於密閉空間工作，水管工可能面臨在空氣中浮游的[[鉛|鉛]]和[[石棉|石棉]]，吸入過多可能分別導致[[鉛中毒|鉛中毒]]及[[肺塵病|肺塵病]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.plumbermag.com/how-to-articles/site_safety_injuries_entry/9_hazards_plumbers_should_be_aware_of |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2020-09-03 |archive-date=2019-08-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190829090026/https://www.plumbermag.com/how-to-articles/site_safety_injuries_entry/9_hazards_plumbers_should_be_aware_of |dead-url=no }}</ref>。如果於高空工作，有可能從高空失足墮下<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1840785/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E8%A3%9D%E6%B0%B4%E7%AE%A1%E5%A4%B1%E8%B6%B3%E5%BE%9E3%E7%B1%B3%E9%AB%98%E5%A2%AE%E4%B8%8B-%E6%B5%B7%E6%B4%8B%E5%85%AC%E5%9C%92%E7%B6%AD%E4%BF%AE%E5%B7%A5%E9%80%81%E9%99%A2%E6%B2%BB%E7%90%86|title=裝水管失足從3米高墮下 海洋公園維修工送院治理|date=2020-08-08|work=頭條日報|accessdate=2020-09-03|archive-date=2020-09-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200903151458/https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1840785/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E8%A3%9D%E6%B0%B4%E7%AE%A1%E5%A4%B1%E8%B6%B3%E5%BE%9E3%E7%B1%B3%E9%AB%98%E5%A2%AE%E4%B8%8B-%E6%B5%B7%E6%B4%8B%E5%85%AC%E5%9C%92%E7%B6%AD%E4%BF%AE%E5%B7%A5%E9%80%81%E9%99%A2%E6%B2%BB%E7%90%86|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

另外，水管工在修理[[污水|污水]]系統時有機會接觸[[排泄物|排泄物]]，有感染各種傳染病的危險<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://oem.bmj.com/content/69/2/140 |title="Infectious disease risks associated with occupational exposure: a systematic review of the literature"  |accessdate=2020-09-03 |archive-date=2020-07-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200709132547/https://oem.bmj.com/content/69/2/140 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。例如[[微生物|微生物]]可以透過[[患者|患者]]的[[糞便|糞便]]或[[嘔吐|嘔吐]]中排泄到廁所，從而污染排污管。導致各種[[传染疾病|傳染性疾病]]，例如[[霍亂|霍亂]]、[[傷寒|傷寒]]、[[肝炎|肝炎]]、[[脊灰|脊灰]]、[[隱孢子蟲病|隱孢子蟲病]]、[[蛔虫病|蛔虫病]]及[[血吸蟲病|血吸蟲病]]。

